{"tid":2478014,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩緊街健 Street Workout？","createTime":"2021-04-06T17:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T23:47:26.000Z","uid":354490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c48cce19d61717d356417001d8966593aca19c","tid":2478014,"uid":354490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"利申我係街健初哥<br />\n玩咗大約半年<br />\n<br />\n初初武肺閂晒GYM房<br />\n慢慢接觸咗街健<br />\n初時由拉唔到引體<br />\n要靠拉力帶做<br />\n再慢慢做到正常引體<br />\n體重同個身板都有一個唔錯嘅進步<br />\n感覺到厚咗好多<br />\n<br />\n另外都意識到Core嘅重要性<br />\nCore差嘅話 <br />\n好多動作都做唔到同唔夠穩<br />\n<br />\n以前喺GYM房<br />\n都無留意過Core<br />\n推完拉完就當做完<br />\n<br />\n去到而家街健<br />\n好似另一個世界咁<br />\n可能有人擔心<br />\n街健靠Bodyweight唔會夠大隻<br />\n但可以放心<br />\nBodyweight都有大把玩法<br />\n絕對夠肌肉撕裂<br />\n只係視乎你做唔做到個啲動作<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打都有玩開街健<br />\n一齊交流下？"},{"pid":"2a6543706515a545ee7c8cb5b6b06f3938285705","tid":2478014,"uid":93897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaa4a4e2c7ac06e5cc99fc94f8356d618f9d5ab","tid":2478014,"uid":354490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a6543706515a545ee7c8cb5b6b06f3938285705","tid":2478014,"uid":93897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae37a76a7f96712bfbfca555a44fe0b882c00cc","tid":2478014,"uid":93897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aaa4a4e2c7ac06e5cc99fc94f8356d618f9d5ab","tid":2478014,"uid":354490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a6543706515a545ee7c8cb5b6b06f3938285705","tid":2478014,"uid":93897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji